license             GPL-2+
maintainers         {jmr @jmroot} openmaintainer
description         an advanced GUI for GNU Arch
long_description \
    ArchWay is a GNU Arch GUI. It follows the unix tradition of \
    small tools doing their work well and cooperating nicely with \
    each other.
